11:
Haha... I applaud the enthusiasm,
but that alone won't be enough.
19:
...Nah, we can stop here. I got what I
needed. Sorry for taking time outta
your day.
24: You can do better than this, Nimbus.
29:
...You don't need to tell me. I know
enthusiasm alone ain't enough.
34: ...Uh-huh. So you want me to train ya?
38:
Yep. You'd be doing me a huge
favor.
42:
Well... I'm not completely against the
idea, but...
45:
What happened to "you can test
your technique with your own two
fists," huh?
52:
All right, fine! So I did say that. But I
know better now. I need to get
stronger, no matter what.
56:
So please, I'm beggin' you... Whip me
into shape!
64:
Gahahaha! Sorry, sorry, I just wanted
to make ya squirm a bit.
67:
But my technique can't be mastered
in a day. It'll push you to your limits...
70: To the verge of death, even.
82:
...Haha, you had a trick like that
hidden up your sleeves this whole
time...
86:
Nimbus! Taiga! What are you two
doing?!
91:
Taiga is powering up an attack
utilizing the majority of his life force.
Nimbus here will receive the full
brunt of it.
94:
This should awaken the power
sleeping within Nimbus. Whatever
happens... he is prepared for the
consequences.
96:
We can only watch and see what
happens, Alk.
136:
Wow... I've never seen you this
powered up before
141:
You didn't... mentioning anything
about HIM, old man...
145:
Ha... Hahaha... Someone's gotta
push you to the verge of death...
remember?
149:
Nimbus. You will be fodder for my
strength.
154:
Hah... Hahaha! You've gotta be
kidding me... I'm actually gonna die
at this rate...
174:
Is this your true self? A wild beast,
driven by fury?
177:
No. Your fists betray you... You do not
crave conflict.
183: Your distaste for violence is plain...
189:
Prince Selenius, such behavior is
unbecoming of royalty
193:
Haha... It's all right. He'll learn
eventually. He's smart like this
mother, after all.
195:
Selenius, do you know why we
Whitetails are big and strong?
197:
It's so we can give our loved ones
nice, big hugs!
199:
Whatever your fears... You needn't
worry. You'll grow up to be big and
strong too!
202:
I don't want strength... for any grand
reason...
205:
I'm just fed up with being at the
mercy of others... Powerless to do
anything but watch...
207:
I don't want anyone else to suffer
like I have. That's all.
216:
Besides, I can't let my pals do all the
work around here.
224:
Heh... Then defend your pride! Show
me what you're capable of!
228:
Haha... Of course. Can't hold back for
training like this, yeah?
241:
So uh... How'd you end up as a
power generator?
246:
It seems the power he awakened is
running amok. The armor he wears
now serves as a limiter to keep it in
check.
249:
He is required to wear it for the time
being. In addition, he's not allowed
to use his power for at least a week.
253:
What, so I can't join the raid on the
lab, huh?!
257:
Did you forget what they said? If you
release that power before you're
ready, you might lose it completely,
or worse... You could even die.
262:
The hell?! They didn't tell me
anything about that! Those damn
geezers!
266:
Somehow I'm not surprised to hear
that...
269:
Guess you'll just have to take a nap
while we handle things.
274:
You've gotta be kidding me! I ain't
sitting out like a kid on time-out!
